Description: This is the Ibanez RGA42MFMT model guitar in flat Dragon Eye burst finish with black hardware in excellent condition. Guitar has Dimarzio pickups installed...Evolution in bridge and another Dimarzio model in neck position. 5-way pickup selector giving you coil tap in 4 position, neck pickup parallel in position 2. 24-fret maple neck with reverse headstock. Ibanez locking tremolo bridge with chrome tremolo arm. Playing action setup is fantastic. I do not use tremolo so guitar is mainly setup to hold tuning. The RGAR42MFMT features a mahogany body with stunning flamed maple top and the legendary thin, Wizard III maple neck, revered for both its playing comfort and unparalleled speed. A Maple fretboard and reversed headstock round out the visuals. Proprietary Quantum pickups are replaced by Dimarzio pickups. Case not included. No international bids, please (USA only). Shipping is $45 to the lower 48 states only (USA)...shipping higher to west coast. Thanks for looking.
Title: Ibanez RGA42MFMT Guitar w/Dimarzio Pups incl. Evolution, Locking Trem, Sunburst
